unittitle_ssm: Adnan Pachachi book collection
abstract_ssm: Consists of selected books and other publications from the personal library of Adnan al-Pachachi (1923-2019), an Iraqi politician and diplomat who also served as an adviser to the government of the United Arab Emirates.  Collection includes titles inscribed to Pachachi from their authors, usually pertaining to the history and current affairs of Iraq or the United Arab Emirates, or titles otherwise related to the life and career of Pachachi and his family.
corpname_ssm: NYU Abu Dhabi, Archives and Special Collections
heading_ssm: Adnan Pachachi book collection
